tc.compiler.tree.visit

Class TreeVisitorBase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tc.compiler.tree.visit.TreeVisitorBase<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeVisitor<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Analyze, Dump, Encode, PreprocessClassDeclarations

    public class TreeVisitorBase<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TreeVisitor<T>
    Base implementation for AST visitors. Performs complete traversal but does nothing. Parameterized by return value.

    The "visit" method is overloaded for every tree node type.
